, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\">考虑如下的二项式形式</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\"><em>n</em>&sup2; +&nbsp;<em>an</em>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<em>b</em>, 且|<em>a</em>| &lt;1000 ， |<em>b</em>| &lt;1000</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\">这里 |<em>n</em>| 是&nbsp;<em>n的绝对值</em><br />e.g. |11| = 11 and |-4| = 4</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\">求对于这个二项式表达式，从n = 0开始，连续产生最多素数的系数a和b的乘积。</p>','2014-02-22 07:19:28','2014-02-22 07:19:28'),(28,'数字螺旋的对角线','<p><span style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\">原题链接&nbsp;</span><a style=\\\"font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\" href=\\\"http://projecteuler.net/problem=28\\\">http://projecteuler.net/problem=28</a></p>\r\n<p style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\">从1开始向右顺时针方向螺旋得到一个5 * 5的螺旋数如下：</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \\\'Times New Roman\\\', \\\'Bitstream Charter\\\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: \\\'courier new\\\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; color: #ff0000;\\\"><strong>21</strong></span><span style=\\\"color: #000000; font-family: \\\'courier new\\\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\\\">&nbsp;22 23 24&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family: \